{"id":2738,"date":"2020-09-21T09:21:24","date_gmt":"2020-09-21T09:21:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/?page_id=2738"},"modified":"2022-08-04T10:36:21","modified_gmt":"2022-08-04T10:36:21","slug":"explorations","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/student-life\/explorations\/","title":{"rendered":"Explorations"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\n<!-- hero -->\n<section class=\"subpage-hero-section\" style=\"background: url('https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/VB21_HALCYON_D1_213-2-copy-1.jpg') center center no-repeat; background-size:cover;background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); background-blend-mode: overlay;\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\n               <h1 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"subpage-hero-h\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">Explorations<\/h1>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<!-- image section -->\n\n<section class=\"image-section   \">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 offset-lg-1\">\n                                  \n                <img class=\"w-100 blue-frame teal-frame\" src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/VB21_HALCYON_D3_643p-e1644493040399.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/>\n                \n                            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 align-items-center d-flex\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n                <div class=\"w-100\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-h teal\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">What are &#8216;Explorations&#8217;? <\/h1>\n                <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Halcyon students are inspired to inquire, communicate, and investigate; the skills that drive success in the rigorous IB MYP and DP Curriculums. We recognise that embracing curiosity is the key to creating an environment where each student can flourish academically and personally. To pioneer an effective learning environment, we do everything we can to embrace students\u2019 individual passions. \r\n<br><br>\r\nOur Explorations Programme invites Grade 6-9 students to select four options per year to explore in weekly two-hour periods. Our Exploration options are built around six learning domains: Creativity, Action, Service, Wellbeing &#038; Citizenship, STEM (science, technology, engineering, mathematics) and Our World. <br><br>\r\nWe also encourage our students to explore a variety of interests through our <a href=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/extracurricular-activities\">Extra-Curricular Activities<\/a>.\r\n<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"text-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n        <div class=\"row\">          \n           \n          <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <div>\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/Copy-of-IMG_4061-e1605873422231.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            <\/div>\n             \n            <div class=\"text-box\">\n              <h4 class=\"section-h smaller-h teal\">Case study: Archaeology <\/h4>\n              <p class=\"section-p\">In one session, Halcyon&#8217;s Archaeology Exploration students took their keen sense of inquiry to new levels by researching the background to artefacts they had discovered themselves. Gabriel (Grade 9) kicked off the session by presenting his own personal finds to the group, sourced from mudlarking on the shore of the River Thames. Students enjoyed carefully handling the artefacts, which ranged from prehistoric arrowheads to clay tobacco pipes to medieval hammered coins.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n           \n          <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <div>\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/unnamed-19-e1602497429861.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            <\/div>\n             \n            <div class=\"text-box\">\n              <h4 class=\"section-h smaller-h teal\">Case study: App maker<\/h4>\n              <p class=\"section-p\">In the final session of their App Maker Exploration App, students used their newly-developed coding skills to carefully control drones. Throughout this period, students mastered the software Scratch and developed their general understanding of coding. Skilfully taking a selfie with the drone to mark the end of this Exploration together, these young learners are an example of how we can embrace technology to expand the boundaries of our creativity.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                     \n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"explorations-section\">\n      <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n          <div class=\"col-lg-4 offset-lg-1\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-h pink\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Robotics Programme<\/h1>\n            <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Participating in an Exploration that spans the course of an academic year, the students in our Robotics Team will go on a journey suitable for all abilities and experiences. Students will explore key concepts using the new Lego Robot Inventor, Robo-Master S1, Sphero, Drones, VR, and more. In the second half of the year, students will be using the VEX IQ and V5 system &#8211; building a robot to compete in an international competition.\r\n<br><br> \r\nThe Robotics Programme supports students in their development of technological expertise as well as teamwork skills. Our students are prepared for the digital technology revolution: the IB embeds STEM skills across the curriculum, and the Robotics Programme, as well as other Explorations options such as Digital and Electronic Music Production, supports their growth into 21st century leaders, communicators, and more. <\/p>\n          <\/div>\n          <div class=\"col-lg-5 offset-lg-1\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n             <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/VB21_HALCYON_D2_456-1.jpg\"\/>\n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"supplies-section  \">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n                <div class=\"row supplies_row bg_gray\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-2 offset-lg-1\">\n                <h3 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"section-h teal\">List of Explorations, 2022\/2023<\/h3>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <span>Session 1<\/span><br><br>\r\nThe Great Grade 6 Adventure (mandatory for Grade 6)<br>\r\nCoding for Beginners<br>\r\nHorse Riding<br>\r\nOral History &#8211; Westminster<br>\r\nSkip the Light Fandango<br>\r\nSquash<br>\r\nTennis<br><br>\r\n<span>Session 2<\/span><br><br>\r\nAn Insider&#8217;s Guide to Unusual Information Sources<br>\r\nDigital Art and Animation<br>\r\nFinance and Investment<br>\r\nIce Skating<br>\r\nLab Science<br> \r\nWriters Circle<br><br>\r\n<span>Session 1 &#038; Session 2<\/span><br><br>\r\nMusic Performance<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> <span>Session 3<\/span><br><br>\r\nActive Citizenship<br>\r\nCross Stitch<br>\r\nDance<br>\r\nHalcyon Podcast<br>\r\nInternational Fiction &#8211; Hidden Voices<br>\r\nMakerspace<br>\r\nWorld Cinema<br><br>\r\n<span>Session 4<\/span><br><br>\r\nAdvanced Coding<br>\r\nConscious Craft Market<br>\r\nCulture and Media<br>\r\nInternational Fiction &#8211; Hidden Voices<br>\r\nLondon Walks<br> \r\nNatural History<br>\r\nVitality<br><br>\r\n<span>Session 3 &#038; Session 4<\/span><br><br>\r\nSchool Show (Actors and Off Stage Direction)<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>                \n                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>  \n                        <div class=\"row supplies_row bg_gray\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-2 offset-lg-1\">\n                <h3 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"section-h teal\">Past Explorations at Halcyon<\/h3>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> Our Explorations offerings change slightly on a year-by-year basis, dependent on student demand and availability. We will be able to bring back some of our previous Exploration options in the future.<br><br>\r\n<span>Past Explorations at Halcyon<\/span><br><br>\r\n&#8211; Debate<br>\r\n&#8211; Cross Country<br>\r\n&#8211; Electronic Music Production<br>\r\n&#8211; Future Entrepreneurs<br>\r\n&#8211; Sculpture<br>\r\n&#8211; Golf<br>\r\n&#8211; Baseline<br>\r\n&#8211; Track and Field Sports<br> \r\n&#8211; App Maker<br>\r\n&#8211; Social Media Management<br>\r\n&#8211; Football <br>\r\n&#8211; Graphic Novel <br>\r\n&#8211; Astronomy<br>\r\n&#8211; Coding<br>\r\n&#8211; Design <br>\r\n&#8211; Alternative Realities<br>\r\n&#8211; Archaeology<br>\r\n&#8211; Cyber Security<br>\r\n&#8211; Baking<br>\r\n&#8211; Flamenco<br>\r\n&#8211; Ice Skating<br>\r\n&#8211; Design your own board game<br>\r\n&#8211; Spin<br>\r\n&#8211; Cupcake Decorating<br>\r\n&#8211; Building Wearable Technology<br> <\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                        <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\"> &#8211; Forensics<br>\r\n&#8211; Bikeability<br>\r\n&#8211; Laboratory Science<br>\r\n&#8211; Track and Field<br>\r\n&#8211; Woodwork<br>\r\n&#8211; Yoga<br>\r\n&#8211; Swimming<br> \r\n&#8211; Basketball<br>\r\n&#8211; EcoSummit<br>\r\n&#8211; Mindfulness<br>\r\n&#8211; Photography<br>\r\n&#8211; Creative Writing<br>\r\n&#8211; Political Ideologies<br>\r\n&#8211; Handball<br>\r\n&#8211; Book binding<br>\r\n&#8211; Art studio <br>\r\n&#8211; Linguistics <br>\r\n&#8211; Speed Cubing (Rubix Cube)<br>\r\n&#8211; Podcasting <br>\r\n&#8211; Introduction to world religion <br>\r\n&#8211; Human rights <br>\r\n&#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.co.uk\/maps\/about\/treks\/#\/grid\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Where In The World Is That?<\/a><br>\r\n&#8211; Eco-psychology<br>\r\n&#8211; Playwriting<br>\r\n&#8211; Cricket<br> \r\n&#8211; Makerspace<br>\r\n&#8211; Research<br>\r\n&#8211; Rock Climbing<br>\r\n&#8211; Trashion<br>\r\n&#8211; Film<br>\r\n&#8211; Bikeability<br><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>                \n                            <\/div>\n        <\/div>  \n                    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"activities-section\">\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\n        <h3 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"section-h text-center teal\">Explorations at Halcyon<\/h3>\n        <div class=\"cubeSlider_wrap\">\n          <div class=\"cubeSlider\">\n                        \n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/IMG_3701-e1605098072562.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">School Show<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/DSC03958-2-e1603797511995.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">App Maker<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/DSC04244-2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">Forensics<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/DSC04553-2-e1603797797641.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">Robotics<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/DSC04882-2-e1603797587553.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">Lab Science<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                              \n              <div class=\"slider_item\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/EDuJHS2XYAEEE-k-1-e1603797545438.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">Cross Country<\/div>\n              <\/div>\n                                 \n          <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"links-section pl-3 pr-3 \">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n                                                <div class=\"col-lg-4 mb-5 col-lg-4\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n                        <a class=\"link d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between teal\" href=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/extracurricular-activities\" target=\"_self\">Extra-Curriculars<svg version=\"1.1\" id=\"Warstwa_1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"18.989px\" height=\"16.98px\" viewBox=\"0 0 18.989 16.98\" enable-background=\"new 0 0 18.989 16.98\" xml:space=\"preserve\"> <path fill=\"